company.name: FI Group
company.description:
The FI Group is a Global Consulting Company specialising in the management of funding incentives such as R&D Tax Reliefs and R&D Grants, with over 20 years of experience in the field it is currently present in 14 countries with 40 offices: Belgium, Brazil, Canada, Chile, Colombia, France, Germany, Italy, Japan, Portugal, Spain, UK, USA and Singapore.

FI Group helps companies finance innovation and secure funding for their Research and Development (R&D) activities through the comprehensive management of R&D Grants and Tax incentives. 
Thanks to our extensive expertise in this area, we advise Start-ups to Large companies on how to maximise their ROI on R&D activities and drive company growth.​

Our optimised financial solutions are based on our specialist understanding of the R&D incentive programs available in each country, as well as the complex legislation that surrounds them.

Our teams consist of more than 1,400 international scientific and technical experts who base their work on Integrity, Professionalism and Empathy; 80% are graduates and PhDs specialized in the sectors in which our clients operate including ICT, manufacturing, chemical, automotive, pharmaceutical, food industry, renewable energy and any other scientific sector. The combination of their technical skills and fiscal expertise are our key to success.

At the global level, FI Group works with over 18,000 satisfied clients, managing more than 30,000 projects a year.
